-她是个特别的女人 -美丽
-But she is an impossible woman. -Beautiful?

3
02:46:58.060 --> 02:47:00.390 
美丽 很美丽
Beautiful? Well, beautiful.

4
02:47:00.480 --> 02:47:03.150 
